    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed every single Sunday. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking just as sharp as the day I brought it home. It drives like a dream and has that 'new car' feel that\u2019s getting harder to find. I\u2019m only selling because I need the space, but I\u2019m looking for a good home for it. Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I'm so proud of this one!",
      "price": 46500.0,
